I want to Die a horrible death. 
I want to get into a care accident and have my face mangled from the impact of my face being crushed by the window sheild.

I want to be so ripped apart that no one can see my face, or distinguish if its really me.
I want to be stabbed by someone that has no reason to stab me.
I want to slowly bleed to death in a room where everyone can see me but no one can speak to me. or get to me.
I want to be hit by a car and be ripped in half by the force.

this is my poem. She should know what im talking about.

"crab."

if my girlfriend turned into a crab.

i wouldnt be sad.

i would just put her in my room.

with a little crab car that would go vroom.

I would take her in my pocket.the the places that i go.

and in the winter. i would make little crab snow.

i would treat her with love and hug her tight as a glove.

i would even make her a little crab mug.

and on her birthdays i would make her a little crab cake.

and then i would surprise her at the pool.

or a little crab lake!

so dont be down if your loved one turns into a crab.

you could just lay down and put them on your abbs.

and with her pinchers she would pinch and stab.

but all in all,

i would still love her as a crab.

So, is that what you call a getaway?
Tell me what you got away with.
Cause I've seen more spine in jellyfish.
I've seen more guts in eleven-year-old kids.
Have another drink and drive yourself home.
I hope there's ice on all the roads.
And you can think of me when you forget your seatbelt,
and again when your head goes through the windshield.

Tonight, We're nothing short of invincible!

Fifth Level of Hell

The river Styx runs through this level of Hell, and in it are punished the wrathful and the gloomy. The former are forever lashing out at each other in anger, furious and naked, tearing each other piecemeal with their teeth. The latter are gurgling in the black mud, slothful and sullen, withdrawn from the world. Their lamentations bubble to the surface as they try to repeat a doleful hymn, though with unbroken words they cannot say it. Because you lived a cruel, vindictive and hateful life, you meet your fate in the Styx.

I wish I didnt have that feeling like my heart is being ripped out..... or that I'm dieing slowly. Sorry to be so meladramatic but thats how I feel as of right now. I dont know why...... no thts not right. I do know why, but it doesnt matter. In the long run things are very trivial. useless, you could say. the only thing that people can hold on to is religion and love. I have one. and I am truly greatful for that. I dont know who I am sopposed to aim my gratitude to, and thats why I dont have the other grip. So, I'm dangling by one arm, in a big world of useless comments, useless thing, and useless people. The only thing that I enjoy as of right now is the sound of my loves voice, but I can't hear her right now, and it hurts..... alot. I love her so much. and I'm sorry for being an asshole to her lastnight, but then when you think about it. There is more to the word love than you might think. I'm in love , I also love all my friends, and my family, and that makes me stronger. but every once in a while there is that weakness that shows his ugly face and pisses off everyone I know. and that is where I'm at right now. I'm sitting here alone. And I really feel like I need someone with me. Truly with me. And it is kind of depressing to think of my family. I'm just waiting for my turn. My Aunt, my Uncle, my Dad........, but there is also an upside to thinking about death. that I got from a movie called big fish. He says that when you think about death, it can help you becasue then you know you can survive anything other than that. Which is a good thought. but not quite right. I just want to move to alaska. My dream. and be with the one woman I love. who makes everything better for me. And brighter, And nicer. She makes all the bad thoughts and confused meanings just wash away. My mind is clearer when I'm with her. Or talking to her. She is everything to me. And I'm being very stupid. But I cant help it. Thats how I am. My stupidity is my personality. And I cant help it. I'm sorry. So... today I am going to go to the park. Try to relax and wait for the love of my life to call me.
